			<abstract>
				<p>Testimony of 19-year-old W.M. and 17-year-old W.R. regarding the roundup of the Jewish community in Csepe (Subcarpathia), the
					Nagyszőllős (Vinohradov) Ghetto, a detailed description of the selection and extermination of prisoner transports in Birkenau,
					their experiences in a labor camp in Hunsfeld, and a death march to Gross-Rosen, Mauthausen, and Bergen-Belsen.</p>
			</abstract>
